e696371129d0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2010034551116822207"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7IfP5OTh0LoNEAMaCTExODU0MDcyOSDt8PrMBjAAOEFAFnITMjAxMDAzNDU1MTExNjgyMjIwN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1772962239.660205", "card_id": "Q_2012066588233335270", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子写作业，关上门安安静静写更好，还是在客厅随时能看到更好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果说专注的话，我觉得孩子自己在房间更合适。但有时会担心，孩子真的在写作业吗？ 你会怎么安排？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e1940716c88cef37d7b631d86b04bfc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2012066588233335270"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7IfP5OTh0LoNEAMaCTExODYxMTc3MyDpuZjNBjAAOBlAF3ITMjAxMjA2NjU4ODIzMzMzNTI3MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1772962239.660756", "card_id": "Q_2013630473239225574", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "山东一幼儿园硬核体能课走红，吊杠前进、跳马、翻越障碍，操场变练兵场，如何评价这一训练模式？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，山东潍坊一家幼儿园的体能课视频在网络引发关注。视频中，孩子们依次完成吊杠前进、跳马、翻越障碍等动作，被网友称为「硬核」幼儿园。 3 月 6 日，潍坊博苑实验幼儿园园长袁女士向记者介绍，视频中的内容是幼儿园日常体能教学的一部分。除跑酷类项目外，学校还开设有平衡车、轮滑、游泳、足球等体育特色课程。 据袁园长介绍，幼儿园针对不同年龄段设定递进式目标：小班通过游戏化课程培养运动兴趣，打牢身体素质基础；中班引入跑酷技巧，练习攀爬、跳跃、悬挂、滚翻等复合型动作；大班则在「赛道」上完成连贯动作展示。 目前幼儿园配备 3 名专职体能教练，均为体育或学前教育专业出身，其中包括国家二级运动员。上课时每班有 2 至 3 名教练主讲，4 名女教师作为助教，保障孩子安全。 谈及家长态度，袁园长表示，起初有家长担心安全问题，但随着对专业防护措施的了解，以及看到孩子体质和胆量的变化，家长逐渐认可。入园前，园方会与家长沟通教育理念；日常接送时家长可观察训练情况；幼儿园还邀请家长作为「观察员」走进课堂；学期末，每位家长会收到一份《体育发展成长报告》，包含专业测评和老师分析。 「核心目标是让孩子爱上运动，养成运动习惯。」袁园长说，希望孩子在运动中变得更加自信勇敢，面对摔倒和挫折时能有积极心态。山东一幼儿园硬核体能课走红，操场变「练兵场」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b5d84d2738ba03bb428181973ede04b9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2013630473239225574"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI7IfP5OTh0LoNEAMaCTExODY2NjY2NiDkmq/NBjAAOLkBQBhyEzIwMTM2MzA0NzMyMzkyMjU1NzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1772962239.661754", "card_id": "Q_2011082967720620482", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "女性如何通过「非虚构写作」，让个人的困境被看见？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "即日起至 3 月 31 日 参与圆桌讨论 和「了不起的女作家」共赴思想之约"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-487551d8d8dd221ab97659fd0cbd8c74_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2011082967720620482"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7IfP5OTh0LoNEAMaCTExODU3OTEwMyDXkYrNBjAAOD5AGXITMjAxMTA4Mjk2NzcyMDYyMDQ4MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1772962239.662029", "card_id": "Q_1963560265229501685", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 775}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "书读得多，就能觉悟吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "书读得多，智慧就多么？「这个孩子读书是块料子，就是有点学呆了。」多读书，就能觉悟吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-76f71b49047fd9329fc1282740b8c381_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_colo